<p>Olivia also took a leaf out of Suki's book opting for another neutral outfit. </p>

<p>The City star, 34, looked every inch the fashion maven in an oversized double breasted blazer, cropped trousers and white heels. </p>

<p>Olivia was joined by her husband Johannes Huebl, who looked dapper in a houndstooth coat. </p>

